To matters diplomacy where Kenya and Somalia have resumed diplomatic relations that had broken down since December of last year. Statements attributed to Somalia&rsquo;s presidency quoting spokesman Abdirashid Hashi as well Kenya&rsquo;s foreign affairs indicates that the relations have been restored after the intervention of Qatar. Kenya has welcomed the new development saying it looks forward to further normalization of relations by the Somalia authorities in regard to trade, communication, transportation and people to people relations.&nbsp;
